body:
## Issues closed
- [#160](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/160) - Next Screen not working

More information about this release can be found on [github](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues?milestone=5).

If you find any bugs please report them on [github](http://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues).

## Issues closed
- [#74](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/74) - Improve release script
- [#162](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/162) - Fix MacPorts paths
- [#120](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/120) - Remove dependency on X11

More information about this release can be found on [github](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues?milestone=4).

## Issues closed
- [#110](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/110) - Noteworthy change in 10.9 Permissions
- [#114](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/114) - App won't run in OSX 10.9 Mavericks
- [#128](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/128) - changed spelling 'me' to 'be'
- [#133](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/133) - Very Minor Typographical Error
- [#129](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/129) - typo in menu
- [#125](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/125) - Reworked the menu icon and added a retina version
- [#118](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/118) - Making ShiftIt work on OS X 10.9 Mavericks
- [#137](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/137) - Add ja localization to release/1.6.1 branch
- [#123](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/123) - Added Japanese localization
- [#139](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/139) - added ja localization for AUTHORIZATION_INFORMATIVE_TEXT_10_8 string
- [#140](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/140) - added ja localization for "Needs Auth" string for 10.8 or earlier. 
- [#143](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/143) - Previous Window (base release/1.6.1)
- [#136](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/136) - Shiftit can't be started on OSX 10.10 (Yosemite)
- [#144](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/pull/144) - Fix NoX11 build
- [#147](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/147) - Accessibility API be enabled
- [#158](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/158) - Fix menu icon for the dark mode in Yosemite
- [#151](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/151) - Add the trick to setup accessibility permission for ShiftIt using sqlite to README.md

More information about this release can be found on [github](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues?milestone=3).

## Issues closed

#36 - Crashes when X11 is not installed on the system
#25 - Doesn't take drawers into account
#60 - Support OSX 10.6 - (was: Can't build ShiftIt 1.6 on OSX Snow Leopard)
#58 - Merge back the X11 support
#55 - Check if AX option is readonly
#56 - Disable actions for windows in fullscreen mode
#57 - Make distinctions between window zooming, filling the screen and fullscreen actions
#59 - Quirks with vertical dual screen
#32 - Added code for incremental sizing
#19 - Multiple Monitor Support (sending windows to other screens)
#67 - Building on OS X Lion + XCode 4.2 from scratch
#70 - The geometry changing actions should respect window anchor
#73 - Add anonymous statistics gathering

More information about this release can be found on the [here](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues?milestone=1&page=1&state=closed).
